      • call

        public final DocumentsCreateVersionResponse call​(String did)
                                          throws OnshapeException
        Calls createVersion method, Create version at the current microversion of the specified workspace or a target microversion. Versions should be created only for tracking the state of a document that will need to be referenced by the user in the future. An application should not use versions as a convenience mechanism for an application to remember document states.
        Parameters:
        did - Document ID
        Returns:
        Response object
        Throws:
        OnshapeException - On HTTP or serialization error

Versions should be created only for tracking the state of a document that will need to be referenced by the user in the future. An application should not use versions as a convenience mechanism for an application to remember document states.
        Parameters:
